0^0
0v0


0^0 tqp will be True when Qopped with something else
0v0 uqp will be Unknown when Qopped with something else
0vv --fqp will be False when Qopped with something else == tan

--kno input is KNOwn == niu
--unk input is UNKnown == isu

0^^ ota will be something Other than True when Anded with something else
00^ --oua will be something Other than Unknown when Anded with something else == fan
00v --ofa will be something Other than False when Anded with something else == uan

v00 --oto will be something Other than True when Ored with something else == uor
^00 --ouo will be something Other than Unknown when Ored with something else == tor
^^0 ofo will be something Other than False when Ored with something else

